},{"pid":"875fc2ed5df63ac5fa5d564fc4adf9372d4613b7","tid":1997793,"uid":23986,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"9a5fd45095315e5a59a05c669ff902836dad00b9","tid":1997793,"uid":174013,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-05-02T02:39:52.000Z","msg":"而家經驗差難搵工<br />\n只會愈黎愈多ON9仔用滲透黎做藉口去做狗"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-02T02:45:26.000Z","msg":"然後暴打市民博升職滲透高層，好似係"},{"pid":"679f323f5786409030041be90eaca43d2d52c12a","tid":1997793,"uid":2404,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-02T02:50:37.000Z","msg":"人工高福利好叫雞唔使錢犯法有人保，唔係咁易架葉師傅"},{"pid":"dbb11e038e3a20c633cc763e957f4075d8d584f5","tid":1997793,"uid":7738,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"cfee95e6db4f73b713541c5b76dd1724fe2bf649","tid":1997793,"uid":52912,"like":0,"dislike":3,"score":-3,"quote":{"pid":"428f0299d0d5185739c6f4d91603c7b036a246a7","tid":1997793,"uid":7738,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-05-02T02:17:25.000Z","msg":"2014？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-05-02T02:23:11.000Z","msg":"應該果時就開始做<br />\n奪軍權先攞到話事權"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-02T03:05:13.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />唔係藍既 有幾多上到指揮官個位<br />\n2014 入去個班大學生 依家都高級督察啦<br />\n今日出緊 7 萬蚊糧啊 未計Housing allowance + OT"},{"pid":"5c3eb59dba812f65c0d78184ae0488baa0728c22","tid":1997793,"uid":3501,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-02T03:17:17.000Z","msg":"識朋友個朋友train緊個陣 已經話自己中立<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"edb95086c5ffcf7fefd1754a0c18124c3592671d","tid":1997793,"uid":232594,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-02T03:51:13.000Z","msg":"入去做細既唔埋堆就比人杯比長官玩，唔夠定力仲比人洗埋腦，要做大又要好多年先做到，仲要一路扮藍唔比人發現，你一有破綻佢地絕對唔會比你升，仲要係藍到出汁個隻，唔係一個容易既事"}]}